				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The Mage / BST duo is VERY effective. If you are thinking of starting this alt on another acct. you can't go wrong with a BST or SHM.  My wife and I duo for rare drops / moderate AA often.  I play 65 Mage (30aa) and she 65 BST (54aa).  The combo of 65% slow and mage nukes is outstanding.  She has ALOT of useful skills... Paragon, Spiritual Dominion, Hobble of Spirits (snare), Slow/criple.  She usually tanks our targets but for the harder ones we can stand back and let her pet tank.  She has alot less days played than me but already has obtained Epic, Ornate: Tunic Legs Boots Cap Gloves, Ancient Prismatic Fistwraps (Avatar), and Pet Focus.  She has gotten most of these do to the lack of Monks/BST on Sol Ro in our LVL/AA range.  Although my wife is a Barbarian, my lil BST is a Iksar and he's great.  BSTs make great partners and fun solo/group alts!<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=457285" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://eqguildpics.freeservers.com/images/meatairsig.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
